#12502
North Garden, at the gate to New Hope, City~
You are at the north gate to the city of New Hope.  A large, metal gate set
in the space between the large stone walls that surround the border of the
town, reaching at least 30 feet high.  You are also at the base of a large
hill, which slopes upwards to the north, and the Castle of New Hope sits on
the top.
