#12504
North Garden~
The way the place is kept gives a certain idea of wealth to the kingdom of
New Hope, with the great invincible castle to the north upon the hill, and
it's surrounding area where you stand.  When a kingdom can put time and money
into more trivial things and give off a good appearance, it shows something
about the richness and prosperity of the land.
