#12505
North Garden Plaza~
The stone-layed path coming from the north and south directions here come into
a plaze area, with a great fountain in the middle, flowing with water day and
night.  Some have chosen this as an alternative to Town Square Central in the
city, as the peaceful and beauty of the garden gives it a much better
atmosphere and sets a nicer mood for all who come to visit the area.
~
